### Get all doctors filtered by specialization
GET https://port4004-workspaces-ws-76zvt.ap21.trial.applicationstudio.cloud.sap/odata/v4/hospital/Doctors?$filter=specialization eq 'Cardiology'

### Get appointments for a specific date
GET https://port4004-workspaces-ws-76zvt.ap21.trial.applicationstudio.cloud.sap/odata/v4/hospital/Appointments?$filter=appointmentDate eq 2026-06-02

### Create a new patient
POST https://port4004-workspaces-ws-76zvt.ap21.trial.applicationstudio.cloud.sap/odata/v4/hospital/Patients
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "ID": "P001",
  "name": "Ravi Kumar",
  "age": 30,
  "gender": "Male",
  "bloodGroup": "O+",
  "phone": "9876543210"
}

### Create a new appointment
POST https://port4004-workspaces-ws-76zvt.ap21.trial.applicationstudio.cloud.sap/odata/v4/hospital/Appointments
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "ID": "A001",
  "appointmentDate": "2026-06-02",
  "status": "Scheduled",
  "doctor_ID": "D001",
  "patient_ID": "P001"
}

### Get patients filtered by blood group
GET https://port4004-workspaces-ws-76zvt.ap21.trial.applicationstudio.cloud.sap/odata/v4/hospital/Patients?$filter=bloodGroup eq 'O+'

### Update appointment status to Completed
PATCH https://port4004-workspaces-ws-76zvt.ap21.trial.applicationstudio.cloud.sap/odata/v4/hospital/Appointments('A001')
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "Completed"
}